---
Source:
  Title: A Year with Hafiz
  Translator: Daniel Ladinsky
  Author: Hafiz
  ISBN: 978-0143117544
  Publisher: Penguin Books
Format: Verse
By: Hafiz
Title: The Season Existence
Description: December 3
---
I like the way you blush, God, the season spring,

the season summer, the season fall, the hour of winter,

and that magnificent season existence!

Yes, I love the way you blush, my Lord, when we are sometimes near.
